Titolo: ARIDA: Backland's Awakening

Anno: 2019

Descrizione: ARIDA: Backland's Awakening (formerly known as Projeto Sertão) is an adventure game and survival video game developed by Aoca Game Lab. The game was released on August 2019, exclusively for Windows, through digital distribution on the Steam platform. The player experiences the journey of Cícera, a young countrywoman who needs to overcome obstacles imposed by hunger and drought in the Brazilian backlands of the 19th century.

Genere: Non specificato


Valutazione: N/A
